To install Hashish you must download:

wxGTK 2.3.2 - http://www.wxwindows.org
Crypto++ 4.2 - http://www.cryptopp.com

Build wxGTK and install it.

Unzip Crypto++ using 'unzip -a crypto42.zip' in 
 a directory named crypto which should be one 
 level below the Hashish dir (../).

Build Crypto++ using provided makefile ('GNUMakefile')
 make -f GNUMakefile

Build hashish using provided makefile:
 make

Copy to your bin dir.  The executable name is 'hashish'


Thanks! configure script coming soon...
